  "instructions": [
    "Place coconut cream in a bowl and add soy sauce, mix well to combine.",
    "Heat olive oil in an air fryer basket at high heat.",
    "Add chopped green onions and garlic cloves to the heated oil and cook until fragrant.",
    "Pour the mixed coconut cream mixture into the air fryer with the cooked vegetables.",
    "Cook on medium-high for about 5 minutes or until slightly thickened, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with black pepper if desired."
